{"tid":1704172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"而家仲諗緊罷唔罷好嘅入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-10T14:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T16:17:12.000Z","uid":46688,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0843adf48dc3567ba0338dddff1483d6ac6548","tid":1704172,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"醫護界嘅可以出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你依家可能諗緊會唔會冇咗份工會唔會成績差，而糾結緊究竟罷唔罷。<br />\n<br />\n但係請你諗下香港，又再諗下義士同烈士，佢哋失去嘅唔單只係收入，佢哋失去嘅可能係未來甚至係性命，而佢哋都係同大家一樣想救翻呢個香港。<br />\n<br />\n其實今日你冇咗份工學少咗嘢對比起義士嘅負擔係少好多，你哋可以有機會再擁有，但係佢哋嘅機會比你更加少，如果你仲愛香港嘅，罷啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再諗藉口畀自己，罷啦。<br />\n<br />\n依家攞起手機，叫你身邊嘅人一齊罷，香港就靠大家了。"},{"pid":"1718e1083b8b17177dff481d15cbef567331b3a5","tid":1704172,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dac02aa3ff32437e2db19412af0f5096214dd6c","tid":1704172,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53f0b0b2396576e9bbff5fc8aa0a4d67c49b985","tid":1704172,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bc97714aa1d61ef2f9b72f552e182a8cc67a09","tid":1704172,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 搬屋師/升降師<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704038</a>"},{"pid":"d16bad379775